REVENUES

BCC SEGMENT REVENUES

CONSIST PRINCIPALLY OF LEASE INCOME FROM EQUIPMENT UNDER OPERATING LEASE AND INTEREST FROM FINANCING RECEIVABLES AND NOTES. BCCS REVENUES DECREASED $21 MILLION AND $43 MILLION IN 2010 AND 2009, DUE TO A SMALLER PORTFOLIO OF EQUIPMENT UNDER

