THE MEASUREMENT OF DEFERRED TAX ASSETS IS REDUCED BY A VALUATION ALLOWANCE IF, BASED UPON AVAILABLE EVIDENCE, IT IS MORE LIKELY THAN

NOT THAT SOME OR ALL OF THE DEFERRED TAX ASSETS WILL NOT BE REALIZED. INCLUDED IN THE NET DEFERRED TAX ASSETS AT DECEMBER 31, 2010 AND 2009 ARE DEFERRED TAX ASSETS IN THE AMOUNTS OF $8,186 AND $7,226 RELATED TO OTHER COMPREHENSIVE LOSS.

WE HAVE PROVIDED FOR U.S. DEFERRED INCOME TAXES AND FOREIGN WITHHOLDING TAX IN THE AMOUNT OF $60 ON UNDISTRIBUTED EARNINGS NOT CONSIDERED PERMANENTLY

REINVESTED IN OUR NON-U.S. SUBSIDIARIES. WE HAVE NOT PROVIDED FOR U.S. DEFERRED INCOME TAXES OR FOREIGN WITHHOLDING TAX ON THE REMAINDER OF UNDISTRIBUTED EARNINGS FROM OUR NON-U.S. SUBSIDIARIES BECAUSE SUCH EARNINGS ARE CONSIDERED TO BE PERMANENTLY

REINVESTED AND IT IS NOT PRACTICABLE TO ESTIMATE THE AMOUNT OF TAX THAT MAY BE PAYABLE UPON DISTRIBUTION.

